sftp bob@ubuntu-vm
# to connect ot a remote host via sftp

# sftp> help                          - to list all available commands
# sftp> ls                            - to list the contents of the current
#                                       working directory
# sftp> get file_to_download.txt      - to download a file from a remote host
# sftp> put file_to_upload.txt        - to upload a file to a remote host
# sftp> bye                           - to end sftp session